{"tid":2277000,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發：法輪功罕有直接表態支持Trump！","createTime":"2020-11-08T07:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T07:27:10.000Z","uid":324569,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dbcccf00560ff5c744b57a50e463556da06f41e4","tid":2277000,"uid":324569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"法輪功最主要網站明慧網，超級罕有直接表態發表編輯部聲明！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>原則和基點一定要明白和清醒</strong><br />\n<br />\n【明慧網二零二零年十一月七日】<br />\n大家好！<br />\n<br />\n看到大家就美國大選的一些交流，不同人有不同認識可以理解，但一些原則和基點一定要明白和清醒：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>這次美國大選是正邪大戰，是神魔之爭。川普是神選之人，要回歸傳統，要解體中共</strong></span>；而另一方是要破壞傳統，要在美國甚至全球搞中共的社會主義那一套。作為修煉人，我們雖然不參與常人的政治，但我們要知道正邪善惡、分清好壞，知道我們要支持誰<strong><span class=\"red\">（川普）</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n明慧編輯部<br />\n二零二零年十一月七日<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.minghui.org/mh/articles/2020/11/7/%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%BA%E9%BB%9E%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E6%98%8E%E7%99%BD%E5%92%8C%E6%B8%85%E9%86%92-414770.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.minghui.org%2Fmh%2Farticles%2F2020%2F11%2F7%2F%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2589%2587%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%25BB%259E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2598%258E%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%25B8%2585%25E9%2586%2592-414770.html&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq73aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=23537993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.minghui.org/mh/articles/2020/11/7/%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%BA%E9%BB%9E%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E6%98%8E%E7%99%BD%E5%92%8C%E6%B8%85%E9%86%92-414770.html</a>"},{"pid":"18f64d021a7cbdc85549f25b935a5c39704aad67","tid":2277000,"uid":342115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"大家有共同敵人 就係中共"},{"pid":"2d13847273ea7977b79ae9a7959e44446433c4ec","tid":2277000,"uid":296613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"正邪之戰！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MsMBei.jpg